The paper deals with video classification using deep neural networks, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a defense framework against adversarial attacks, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG) and security and privacy (cs.CR). The paper also involves denoisers, which is a topic related to multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper proposes a method to distinguish between adversarial and benign videos, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
